name: American Documents® 41mm Leather Strap Watch
description: Just like our very first mantel clocks, 165 years ago, our American Documents® collection layers American ingenuity and craftsmanship with European precision to create a truly amazing timepiece. This American-made watch is drop forged in US-sourced stainless steel and hand finished to a brushed satin with a highly polished top ring. The Gorilla® Glass 3 protects the blue sub-second dial and gold-plated Swiss movement with its high resistance to scratches and sharp content damage. The rich brown leather strap is made with American hides by American craftsmen. And right down to the details, the “Aged Waterbury Brass” case back coin and crown insert honor our original stamped brass clocks from 1854. Each American Documents™ watch arrives in a solid cherry wood case that is hand rubbed to a natural finish. An inlaid magnetic closure and brass hinges secure the felt-lined custom setting for the rare occasions when the watch is not being worn. As seen in Hodinkee, aBlogtoWatch, Forbes, Adweek, Gear Patrol, Worn & Wound, Cool Hunting and many more...

name: Waterbury Traditional Automatic Open-Heart Dial 42mm Stainless Steel Bracelet Watch
description: We applied a new movement to an old favorite, honoring our watchmaking heritage in Waterbury, Connecticut. Visible through the watch face is a tried-and-true 21-jewel automatic movement. Powered by your motion, the movement has a 40-hour power reserve and can also be wound with the crown. The stainless-steel case and bracelet are complemented by its blue open-heart dial. Like our craftsmanship and commitment to our heritage, some things are automatic.

name: Waterbury Classic Chronograph 40mm Leather Strap Watch
description: There is strength in tradition. This collection is an update to a true classic — a timepiece honoring our roots with ageless style. A testament to our commitment to craftsmanship and watchmaking, the Waterbury Classic Chronograph is well-suited for everyday wear with its stainless steel case, silver-tone dial and tan leather strap with tweed fabric lining and quick-release spring bars.

description: Just like our very first mantel clocks, 165 years ago, our American Documents® collection layers American ingenuity and craftsmanship with European precision to create a truly amazing timepiece. This American-made watch is drop forged in US-sourced stainless steel and hand finished to a brushed satin with a highly polished top ring. name: Marlin® Automatic 40mm Leather Strap Watch
description: Our iconic 1960s Marlin® case gets an aesthetic refresh. Ticking inside is a tried and true 21-jewel automatic movement, creating a contemporary timepiece that honors our watchmaking history. Powered by your motion, the movement has a 40-hour power reserve and can also be wound with the crown like our original Marlin® watch. True to our original Marlin design, the stainless-steel case and blue dial are complemented by a classic brown natural leather strap and its iconic domed acrylic crystal.

name: TIMEX IRONMAN GPS Watch
description: Just select your workout and start. Quickly connect to GPS for real-time pace, speed and distance. After your workout, upload and charge with the universal micro USB cable. Ready. Set. Go. PC/MAC REQUIRED

name: Q Timex Reissue Digital LCA 32.5mm Stainless Steel Bracelet Watch
description: Call us nostalgic, but we love digging into our archives. This time we found a digital watch from the late 80s we just had to bring back. Our Q Timex Reissue Digital LCA, liquid crystal analog, recreates the original right down to the unique digital/analog display. We’ve updated it with a gold-tone stainless-steel case, but kept the pre-INDIGLO® single-bulb backlight for a truly retro vibe.

name: Command Urban™ 47mm Silicone Strap Watch
description: Our Command Urban™ collection is proof of our legendary durability. We paired a blue translucent retro case shape and design with a solid top ring and blue translucent silicone strap, giving a new look to our shock-resistant, water-resistant favorite. The large display is easy to read and our Timex World Time technology provides the time zone in 64 major urban areas around the world.

name: Command™ LT 40mm Silicone Strap Watch
description: Our Command™ LT is a digital watch with bold style. The reimagined design holds a black metallic top ring and matching tonal, segmented negative LCD display. The right-sized 40mm black resin case is paired with our most wearable soft silicone black strap. And, of course, we added our INDIGLO® backlight to prove great watchmaking can be digital.

name: Timex Command™ 47mm Silicone Strap Watch
description: Even if nothing shocks you, life can be hard on your watch. That is why we built Command™ 47 to ISO shock-resistant standards with proprietary digital technology and a soft green silicone rubber quick-release strap. The oversized green case with yellow accents is water resistant up to 200 meters — protecting the digital timers, alarms and our INDIGLO® backlight.

name: Timex Metropolitan R 42mm Leather and Silicone Strap Watch
description: Metropolitan R has all the functionality you need including up to 2 weeks of battery life. This sleek design boasts an impressive AMOLED display that you can customize with over 20+ dial designs. Plus, 24/7 activity and sleep tracking for your health and fitness goals, on-board GPS, optical heart rate sensor, notifications and much more. This is the perfect smartwatch to fit your busy lifestyle. The brown leather and silicone combination strap is complemented by a black metal case and scratch-resistant Gorilla Glass™ lens.

name: Timex Metropolitan S 36mm Silicone Strap Watch
description: Metropolitan S has all the functionality you need including up to 2 weeks of battery life. This sleek design boasts an impressive AMOLED display that you can customize with over 20+ dial designs. Plus, 24/7 activity and sleep tracking for your health and fitness goals, on-board GPS, optical heart rate sensor, notifications and much more. This is the perfect smartwatch to fit your busy lifestyle. The black silicone strap is complemented by a black metal case and scratch-resistant Gorilla Glass™ lens.

name: TIMEX® IRONMAN® R300 GPS 41mm Silicone Strap Watch
description: We know there’s no finish line. That’s why we built our TIMEX® IRONMAN® R300 GPS watch for constant improvement. Overbuilt but not overpriced, this smartwatch is packed with a powerhouse battery, guided workouts from elite athletes and coaches, continuous optical heart rate monitoring and more, delivering a range of performance metrics to help you tune your workouts and reach your running goals. The crisp sunlight-readable display, simple user interface and robust mobile connectivity come together for a made-for-sports smartwatch that will have no trouble keeping up with you.

name: iConnect® by Timex Premium Active 36mm Mesh Bracelet Smartwatch
description: Goals are easier to reach than ever with features like heart rate tracking, sleep and activity tracking and mobile notifications. Our iConnect® Premium Active smartwatch is where fitness meets fashion with its vibrant touchscreen, 36mm silver case and silver mesh strap. Connect to your phone using the iConnect® by Timex 2 app available for iOS and Android. (Requires iOS 10.0 and above or Android 6.0 and above)

name: iConnect® by Timex Pro 43mm Leather Strap Smartwatch
description: Utilizing a high-definition AMOLED display to bring custom-designed digital elements to life, iConnect® Pro includes core smartwatch features like activity tracking, sleep tracking, heart rate monitoring and notifications right on your wrist. Thanks to the vibrant touchscreen and custom watch faces, this is your everyday dressed up option featuring a 43mm gunmetal case and brown leather strap. Connect to your phone using the iConnect® by Timex 2 app available for IOS and Android. (Requires iOS 10.0 and above or Android 6.0 and above)

name: Leather Folio Case and Passport Holder For Two Watches
description: Be ready for each new adventure. Designed with the jet-setter in mind, our black leather watch case with soft-touch lining holds two watches and your passport, keeping your watches safe and passport secure while traveling.

name: Leather Mini-Folio Case For Two Watches
description: Carefully transport and store your watches with a case crafted to keep your watch protected. Our black leather case holds up to two watches, with soft-touch lining and a zipper to keep your watches safe.

name: Canvas and Leather Roll For Four Watches
description: Have a watch for every adventure? Explore wildly while keeping your watches safe. Our black canvas watch roll with leather trim and soft-touch lining holds up to 4 watches and rolls up for a compact way to carry your watches anywhere.

name: Black Leather Watch Pouch
description: Keep your favorite watch safe when it’s not on your wrist. Our black leather case with soft-touch lining holds one watch for a safe and compact way to protect your watch.

name: Marlin® Automatic 40mm Leather Strap Watch
description: Our iconic 1960s Marlin® case gets an aesthetic refresh. Ticking inside is a tried and true 21 jewel automatic movement, creating a contemporary timepiece that honors our watchmaking history. Powered by your motion as you wear the watch, the movement can store a maximum 40 hours of energy. If motionless longer than 40 hours, wind the watch using the crown until you feel resistance, set it and place the watch back on your wrist where every motion will provide energy for the movement. True to our original Marlin® design, the stainless steel gold-tone case and black dial are complemented by a classic black leather strap, featuring leather from the S.B. Foot Tanning Company, and its iconic domed acrylic crystal. KEEP ON TICKING®

name: Waterbury Classic Automatic Open Heart Dial 40mm Leather Strap Watch
description: We applied a new movement to an old favorite. Ticking inside is a tried-and-true 21-jewel automatic movement for a more accurate, longer lasting timepiece. Powered by your motion as you wear the watch, the movement can store a maximum 40 hours of energy. If motionless longer than 40 hours, wind the watch using the crown until you feel resistance, set it and place the watch back on your wrist where every motion will provide energy for the movement. The two-tone stainless steel case with rose gold-tone accents is complemented by its black open heart dial and gray natural leather strap. Like our craftsmanship and commitment to our heritage, some things are just automatic.

name: Waterbury Traditional Automatic 42mm Stainless Steel Bracelet Watch
description: We applied a new movement to an old favorite. Ticking inside is a tried-and-true 21 jewel automatic movement for a more accurate, longer lasting timepiece. The stainless steel case is complemented by its white dial and stainless steel bracelet. Like our craftsmanship and commitment to our heritage, some things are just automatic.

name: Marlin® Automatic x Peanuts Featuring Snoopy and Woodstock 40mm Leather Strap Watch
description: Our iconic 1960s Marlin® case gets an aesthetic refresh. Ticking inside is a tried and true 21 jewel automatic movement, creating a contemporary timepiece that honors our watchmaking history. Powered by your motion, the movement has a 40-hour power reserve and can also be wound with the crown. The sleek monochromatic design is given a playful update with Snoopy and Woodstock on the dial. True to our original Marlin®, the stainless-steel case and silver-tone dial are complemented by a classic black natural leather strap and its iconic domed acrylic crystal.

name: Marlin® Automatic California Dial 40mm Leather Strap Watch
description: Our iconic 1960s Marlin® gets an aesthetic update with a California dial. This vintage dial treatment originated in the 1930’s and uniquely displays half of the dial in Roman numerals and half in Arabic numerals. Ticking inside is a tried and true 21 jewel automatic movement with an exhibition case back, creating a contemporary timepiece that honors our watchmaking history. Powered by your motion, the movement has a 40-hour power reserve and can also be hand-wound with the crown. True to our original Marlin® design, the stainless-steel case and vintage California dial artwork are complemented by a classic brown natural leather strap and its iconic domed acrylic crystal.
